original_title: モーニング娘。コンサートツアー 2005春 〜第六感 ヒット満開!〜
overview: Morning Musume.'s Ishikawa Rika's Graduation Concert held at Nippon Budokan.  Morning Musume. is a Japanese idol girl group part of Hello! Project, produced by Tsunku. "Dai 6 Kan Hit Mankai!" features a concert from their 2005 spring tour. It was filmed May 7 at Nippon Budokan and was also the graduation concert for 4th generation member Ishikawa Rika.
title: Morning Musume. 2005 Spring ~Dai 6 Kan Hit Mankai!~
